Review: I love the keyboards and what not it looks so awesome but just need some more themes to choose from or more customization choices.

This keyboard is good but it really needs more theme.
Wish for more keyboard themes to come.
But can we have more themes for the keyboard =)
Anyway I couldn't thank SwiftKey any better for such an amazing keyboard, just wish that they will come out with better features and personalization along with new themes!

I was hoping to have a good heart symbol with the key board because that's something a girl uses a lot for commenting on photos and stuff like that if added, and I would be much happier with the application and rate it a five stars but, there are not a lot of color choices for your keyboard......
The functional keys in the bottom: shift, enter, backspace etc. come in a certain color with every theme. I would like this color to be fully customisable to make it fit my phone's theme better.
Needs better emotes and I thinks that's it except maybe custom keyboards.
If you could customize the keyboard to a different colour for all keyboards, I will give you 5 stars.
